  "title": " test(searchbox): remove needless snapshot",
  "body": "This removes a snapshot with an inline assertion, since it's very small, and avoids the indirection. In the future if we don't want to write an assertion, I'd suggest the following flow:\r\n\r\n1. add toMatchInlineSnapshot\r\n2. change snapshot to real assertion\r\n3. profit",
